(167, 1, '2020-10-13 05:06:36', '2020-10-13 05:06:36', '<p>[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1603973510976{background-image: url(http://angur.local.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/about.jpg?id=503) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" el_class=\"Main_Page_Banner\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"page_name_container about-page-container\"][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=\"About us\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center\" css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page_name\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page_name_para\"]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">At Angur, we ensure that the natural taste and the nutritional value of Dals are never compromised. We give utmost importance to purity and hence all the ingredients are selectively picked. With Angur, you’ll never go wrong in preparing delicious and mouth-watering dishes for your loved ones!</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"what_we_do_section container\"][vc_column el_class=\"who-we-are-section\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page_section_title\"]Who We Are[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page-para\"]Angur brings to you superior quality dals straight from the fertile land of Gujarat. The journey of Angur as a brand began five decades ago in 1965. During those days, people were habituated to buy loose products from kirana stores and thus it became very challenging for us to convince them and change their buying habits. But with our superior quality product, consistency, advanced processing, and full-proof packaging, we succeeded in building a trust for the brand and today we stand true as we say, “guniyal naari ni ek maatra pasand”.</p>\r\n<p>At Angur, our mission is to spread happiness beyond kitchens and we’re happy that the young generation in our team has also inherited the same. We thus strive to excel more and more in providing best quality products that helps consumers stay fit and healthy.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"487\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"what_we_do_image who_we_are_image\" css=\".vc_custom_1603966049045{margin-top: 70px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"what_we_do_section why_choose_us\" css=\".vc_custom_1602566052956{background-image: url(http://angur.local.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/about_us_bg.png?id=171) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"container\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page_section_title\"]Why Choose Us[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"what-we-do-para\"]<span id=\":h7.co\" class=\"tL8wMe EMoHub\" dir=\"ltr\">Because we never compromise on purity and taste</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page-para\"]<strong>Purity - </strong> All the ingredients at Angur are selectively picked and preserved with utmost care. Angur has always never believed in the compromising nutritional value obtained from the Dals and thus Angur Toor Dal and Angur Chana Dal are 100% pure. With all the nutritional value, we also emphasize on hygienic processing without any human interference.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Taste - </strong> Full-proof modern packaging keeps the freshness intact to maintain the taste as well as keeps moisture away to give a storage life.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Time - </strong> Angur Dals because of its purity and freshness has the lowest cooking time. Angur Toor Dal and Angur Chana Dal thus takes less time to cook compared to other Dals. This also enables you to save energy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"container images_container\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"173\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"fadeInUp\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"175\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"fadeInUp\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"174\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"fadeInUp\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"what_we_do_section container\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page_section_title\"]What We Do[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"what-we-do-para\"]At Angur, our mission is to spread happiness beyond kitchens.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"500\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"what_we_do_image\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"page-para\"]Angur is loved for its superior quality TOOR DAL. And for all the love received over the years, we have also introduced Angur Chana Dal and Angur Besan to our range of products.</p>\r\n<p>We ensure that the inherent qualities and the nutritional value of Dals are never compromised. This gives us all the health benefits that we are looking for. Angur Dals thus help you maintain your health and keeps you fit. We also emphasize on maintaining the consistency of taste. With our advanced facility, processing is done without any human interference. Full-proof modern packaging adds to the freshness and to keep moisture away giving it a longer storage life. With its unmatched quality and consistent taste, Angur has become a household name not just in India but across countries like USA, Canada, UK, Kuwait, Dubai, Bahrain, Fiji, Ireland, Indonesia, and Malaysia.</p>\r\n<p>With Angur, you\'ll never go wrong in preparing delicious and mouth-watering dishes for your loved ones.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\