(622, 1, '2020-11-02 10:33:30', '2020-11-02 10:33:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Diet plays a very important when it comes to leading a healthy lifestyle. What you eat and when you eat are the two questions that each and every individual should address on a day-to-day basis. As per studies, adult men need about 56 grams of protein a day while adult women need about 46 grams a day to suffice the requirements of the body. And so, If you are a vegetarian or if you are trying to incorporate plant-based protein into your regimen, then Dals are definitely your best bet! Protein in dal is the way to go!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Protein-rich lifestyle with Angur Dals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '207-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-11-02 10:33:30', '2020-11-02 10:33:30', '', 207, 'http://angur.local.com/207-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
