(650, 1, '2020-11-23 11:56:18', '2020-11-23 11:56:18', 'Angur Chana Dal is hygienically processed under controlled supervision. Full-proof modern packaging adds to the freshness and to keep moisture away giving it a longer shelf life.\n\nWith the all new Angur Chana Dal, you\'ll never go wrong in preparing delicious and mouth-watering dishes for your loved ones. Pick one now!\n\n<strong class=\"ultitle\">Key Features of Angur Chana Dal:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Reduces bad cholesterol</li>\n<li>Diabetes friendly</li>\n<li>Reduces Iron deficiency</li>\n<li>Strengthens bones</li>\n<li>Regulates blood pressure</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n100% Pure Chana Dal\n\nSelectively Picked\n\n✔ Monitored Production\n\n✔ Advanced Processing\n\n✔ Full-proof Packaging', 'Angur Chana Dal', '<strong>Angur Chana Dal</strong>Available in: 500g<br>\n<p class=\"para\">Chana dal is a part of every household across India. With all the hands-on experience, Angur brings you the finest quality Chana Dal that is full of nutritional value and health benefits apart from its pure taste. Angur Chana dal is a rich source of dietary fibres and contains very less amount of polyunsaturated fats. It has a low glycaemic index (GI), which makes it suitable for diabetics and is known to increase glucose tolerance. Angur Chana Dal is also rich in several vitamins and is low in cholesterol.</p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '356-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-11-23 11:56:18', '2020-11-23 11:56:18', '', 356, 'http://angur.local.com/356-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(651, 1, '2020-11-23 13:27:46', '2020-11-23 13:27:46', '<strong class=\"ultitle\">Key Features of Angur Urad Dal:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Urad dal is recognised as the most nutritious of all pulses</li>\n<li>It is the main ingredient of papads, dosas and idlis</li>\n<li>Easily digestible</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n', 'Angur Urad Dal', '<strong>Angur Urad Dal</strong>Available in: 500g\n<p class=\"para\">Angur Urad Dal is a commonly used dal in the Indian kitchen. Angur Urad Dal is extremely nutritious and high in protein. It is a premium quality product that can be used regularly for cooking purpose. It has various positive impacts on one\'s health and body.</p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '324-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-11-23 13:27:46', '2020-11-23 13:27:46', '', 324, 'http://angur.local.com/324-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(652, 1, '2020-11-23 13:25:25', '2020-11-23 13:25:25', 'The iron, folic acid, calcium, magnesium, potassium, and B vitamins in Angur Toor Dal help meet the daily vitamin and mineral requirements of the body.\n\nAt Angur, we ensure that the inherent quality and the nutrient values of dals are never compromised. With advanced processing and hygienic packaging we make sure that Angur Toor Dal retains the original health value stored in it.', 'Angur Moong Whole', '<strong>Angur Moong Whole</strong>Available in: 500g<br>\n<p class=\"para\">Angur Moong Whole Dal has immeasurable benefits. It has constituted an important part of Indian cuisine. It can fulfil the nutritional and dietary requirements of an entire meal. It has various positive impacts on one\'s health and body.</p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '352-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-11-23 13:25:25', '2020-11-23 13:25:25', '', 352, 'http://angur.local.com/352-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
